OL,3,CChildren sent to UK due to lack of
OL,4,Cfoster parents, say advocacy group
OL,6,F"He had to start at a new school,
OL,7,Flearn to make new friends and learn to
OL,8,Ftrust people elsewhere.
OL,10,F"That message that nobody in Jersey
OL,11,Fcan provide a home for a Jersey child
OL,12,Fis problematic and we'd like to see
OL,13,Fthat change."
OL,15,FThere are currently 19 children in
OL,16,Ffoster care on the island and the
OL,17,FGovernment says it needs around 12
OL,18,Fmore families to meet the current
OL,19,Fdemand for places.
