OL,3,CChildren sent to UK due to lack of
OL,4,Cfoster parents, say advocacy group
OL,6,FShe says: "Every single child that has
OL,7,Fstayed with us has shaped us, they've
OL,8,Ftaught us stuff, we've had the
OL,9,Fprivilege of inviting them into our
OL,10,Fhome and sharing really special times,
OL,11,Fit's been really rewarding."
OL,13,FThe Minister for Children, Connetable
OL,14,FRichard Vibert, told ITV Channel that
OL,15,Fnine families have recently enquired
OL,16,Fabout fostering and seven of these
OL,17,Fapplications are progressing.
